{"type": "article", "id": 34408, "title": "作为一把尺，这块波纹板可能是认真的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-13T23:45:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34826, "name": "Dsignedby"}, {"id": 21517, "name": "Arnaud Lapierre"}, {"id": 34827, "name": "Erdem Selek"}, {"id": 34828, "name": "Reinier de Jong"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 157, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161113215158NUGck4JHv2dVQxFe.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Lunch on the Go: Snack Cup by Alexis Michael</h3><p>因为过快的生活节奏，有时人们不得不在车上急急忙忙解决自己的一餐，Alexis Michael 为此特别设计了这个零食杯，让人能够安心地填饱肚子而不用担心车厢变得狼藉的问题。这款产品本身是一个瓶托，最上方是一个防尘盖，中间两层的设计和便当盒有些类似，只要轻轻旋转就可以吃到里面的食物了。Michael 还特意将凹槽边缘设计成了弧形，防止食物因车辆移动而溅洒出来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215233E5PItmb6SoMFvwj4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215232TPXx2rhlGpaNEBdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215233kotL0rZghIKm17qx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215233YCDcx3VRFalE1pk2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611132152328tzhRxb91veXC6BY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215232AX1ciYVUMOqz9Zrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kitch’T by Dsignedby</h3><p>为了帮助居住空间并不大的年轻人也能拥有一个功能齐全而且可以让朋友们聚在一起的用餐空间，塞尔维亚品牌 <a href=\"http://www.dsignedby.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dsignedby</a> 带来了这款名为 Kitch’T 的家具。它是以品牌旗下的 Table T 为基础设计而成的一站式厨房，最上方是一个自带灶台可丽耐台面，上面还内置了充电器和插座。打开下方那些没有把手、采用按压式开关设计的木制橱门，小冰箱、洗碗机等设备一应俱全，只要连接上水电供应就可以使用了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215256BAnVfhj9bq185sPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215258L4cp8AdEkutTh1gY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611132152589gtTLpKeAx6mUkn5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215256NksQKmRLf9hVAPUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215258LwuMglXEAZkqRTGK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Corrugated Ruler by Erdem Selek</h3><p>作为常见的办公用品，普通的直尺造型总是给人一目了然的存在感，土耳其设计师 <a href=\"http://www.erdemselek.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Erdem Selek</a> 对此有一番不同的见解：由于越来越多的人选择在家中办公，他希望打造一款可以融入环境当中的文具。虽然这套名为 Corrugated Ruler 的直尺没有遵循传统用线条和数字作出标记，但人们依然可以通过按照一厘米分隔的波纹状表面开展工作。在不使用的时候，这些纯色的尺子就像是装饰品一样，给办公环境带来了一种静谧的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611132153242HM8fUB6SRpq0kDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215322HwLngaCY0QzZjxcI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215321Zbe4iVwSXUxAG6ck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215322nhkTNa5xBAl3bPDJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Shield by Arnaud Lapierre</h3><p>法国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://arnaud-lapierre.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Arnaud Lapierre</a> 最近带来了一套仿佛把数码图像实体化的花瓶系列。类似卷轴的圆柱形花瓶后附带了一张颇具像素风的弧形“屏风”，这个看起来像是保护花朵的设计让作品因此得名为 <a href=\"http://www.aybar-gallery.com/index.php/works/detail/168/shield\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shield</a>。得益于它独特的造型，如果花朵搭配得当，每换一个角度都会带来不同的装饰效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215337Q4MCiAI7hqlGnHsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215337RyEXalAFgPMH31BV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215338DhwmKavY3120XJtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215338FxtMyUls8J54iro7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hilt by Reinier de Jong</h3><p>铁锹和铲子把手处的十字形在荷兰语中被称作 Hilt，设计师 <a href=\"http://www.reinierdejong.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reinier de Jong</a> 根据这个部分，为家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.stilst.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stilst</a> 设计了这款同名的边桌。中央的弯木给人一种会倾覆的紧张感，实际上借助底部白色金属框架的支撑，它能够很安稳地站在平面上。有了穿过桌面的把手，移动边桌的方式也变得更方便有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215445tVOep1yGhzSIoqb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215445cYwFh63RxJpm1jfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668056\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215445TLPwheUb19vDfYiK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215445EDoycgtem2TnrOhW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TTFM by STUDIOBIUM</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>这组极简风格的牛奶包装是日本设计师 <a href=\"http://studiobium.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yoshifumi Yokoyama</a> 为泰国品牌 Thai Tip Fresh Milk（TTFM）打造的形象设计。即便没有过多的说明，以字母 M 为原型设计的 logo 本身就是一个相当醒目的元素。设计师更是安排它占据整面牛奶盒身或是瓶身上的标签，通过这种方式传递出产品的纯粹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215359vfaLlwqz25dX8otx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215359bkF6pWwSVo54Btxr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215359GVvjYDJWZdxhS2rc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161113215359beWAyclX6LkVoDP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}